dct_description_sm: 2 bar scales on map, given in "Milliaria Germanica communia" and "Milliaria Gallica communia."
North oriented toward right of sheet.
Decorative cartouches, compass roses, rhumb lines, figures, ships, sea monsters.
Shows Indonesian islands: Maluku, Halmahera, Ternate, Tidore, Bachlian; and vegetation.
Inset map: "Bachian I."; view of early Dutch settlement of Bachian.
